BirthData.DetailedNotes: Government official. Indefatigable, dedicated, easy going, wise, cracking rube image. Tough tactician, second most powerful man in government. Blue denim Machiavelli, had too many fingers in too many pies. If he couldn't win himself he'd run his cousin. Aptitude for administration and planning. Penetrating eyes, unlined apple cheeked face, unreavealing of emotions. Casual clothes, self depreciative. CB 77. .
